Summary: round bottom with top sticking up
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were out on a boat in Lake Murray,having fun with 6 people and I wanted to try to take a picture of the bright stars. I picked a spot and took the picture and saw what I took and showed my husband immediately. We both lookede up at the sky and saw nothing. I showed the others on the boat and they looked up and saw nothing either. I've kept the pic every since. Didn't know what to do with it.
